Amateur Photographer - November 15, 2014  UK

84 Pages | True PDF | English | 29 MB

Amateur Photographer is the world's oldest weekly magazine for photography enthusiasts. With its unique weekly format, it is the first for news and events, plus features on techniques, equipment tests and darkroom advice. It appeals to those interested in buying and learning about digital and film photographic equipment, wanting advice on improving their technique, and learning about the greats in photography. 

==============================================

Digital SLR Photography - December 2014  UK

176 Pages | True PDF | English | 35 MB

Digital SLR Photography addresses the needs of today's photographer in a lively, informative and stylish format. Dedicated to digital SLR photographers of all abilities, from beginner through enthusiast to professional it will inform and entertain you through a unique blend of technique articles, inspirational images, news and authoritative reviews. Covering topics such as landscapes, portraits and close up photography, this magazine provides a focused and comprehensive read guaranteed to help you get the most out of your photography.

PhotoPlus The Canon Magazine - December 2014  UK

118 Pages | True PDF | English | 29 MB

Photoplus magazine is entirely devoted to everything to do with Canon cameras. The magazine has all the latest need to know information on how to get the best out of your Canon Digital SLR camera as well as useful advice and tricks to improve your own photography skills. There will also be helpful honest product review sections for those readers who want to buy the latest new cameras as well as PC accessories and software products.
